data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home just completed, conveniently located near shopping. Built only a year ago. Open concept floor plan. Wood look vinyl planks throughout, with carpet in the bedrooms. Granite counters. Stainless steel appliance package included (26cf side by side fridge w/ ice & water, self-cleaning glass top range, dishwasher and OTR microwave). Fully fenced yard and 2 large storage sheds in backyard.
